    Base Endpoint: api.scryfall.com
    Requests need User-Agent & Accept Header (application/json)
    User-Agent needs to be set dynamically -> build a client system

Sets
    /sets -> All Sets
    /sets/tcgplayer/<id> -> Set with TCGPlayer API Id
    /sets/<uuid> -> Set with Scryfall UUID

Cards
    /cards/search -> List objects of cards matching query
    /cards/named -> Single Card based on name
    /cards/autocomplete -> Catalog object of 20 english cards matching name query
    /cards/random -> Random cardRequest based on optional query
/cards/collection -> Collection of Cards based on posted cardRequest identifier json

    /cards/<code>/<number>(/<lang>) -> Single Card based on set code and collector number with optional lang
/cards/multiverse/<id> -> Single Card based on Multiverse ID
/cards/mtgo/<id> -> Single Card based on MTGO ID
/cards/arena/<id> -> Single Card based on Arena ID
/cards/tcgplayer/<id> -> Single Card based on TCGPlayer ID
/cards/cardmarket/<id> -> Single Card based on Cardmarket ID
/cards/<id> -> Single Card based on Scryfall ID
All of the Single Card based api endpoints all have /rulings to get rulings for a cardRequest

    /symbology -> List of all Card Symbols
    /symbology/parse-mana -> Scryfall Interpretation of given mana cost

    /catalog/cardRequest-names -> Catalog of all english nontoken cardRequest names
    /catalog/artist-names -> Catalog of all artist names
    /catalog/word-bank -> Catalog of all english words that can exist on a magic cardRequest
    /catalog/supertypes -> Catalog of all super types
    /catalog/cardRequest-types -> Catalog of all cardRequest types
    /catalog/artifact-types -> Catalog of all artifact types
    /catalog/battle-types -> Catalog of all Battle Types
    /catalog/creature-types -> Catalog of all Creature Types
    /catalog/enchantment-types -> Catalog of all Enchantment Types
    /catalog/land-types -> Catalog of all Land Types
    /catalog/planeswalker-types -> Catalog of all Planeswalker Types
    /catalog/spell-types -> Catalog of all Spell Types
    /catalog/powers -> Catalog of all possible powers of a creature/vehicle
    /catalog/thoughnesses -> Catalog of all possible powers of a creature/vehicle
    /catalog/loyalties -> Catalog of all possible loyalties of planeswalkers
    /catalog/keyword-abilities -> Catalog of all keyword abilities
    /catalog/keyword-actions -> Catalog of all keyword actions
    /catalog/ability-words -> Catalog of all ability words
    /catalog/flavor-words -> Catalog of all flavor-words
    /catalog/watermarks -> Catalog of all watermarks

    /bulk-data -> List of all bulk data objects
    /bulk-data/<id> -> Bulk Data object based on id
    /bulk-data/<type> -> Bulk Data object based on type





